          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">If, at a different time, you click to play the same video, it should play immediately from your hard-disk.</para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName">Video display too small?</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">If the video dialog is too small, drag the right and bottom sides of the dialog to increase its size.</para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName">Where do the Videos download to?</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The default path is <text styleclass="VariableName">&lt;LocalAppData&gt; \ Tutorials\ </text><text styleclass="BodyText BI">*</text><text styleclass="VariableName">.mp4</text></para>
